name: Timeline Photos
message: Anong tawag nyo sa prutas na ito?

name: ‘Diktadurya at hindi demokrasya ang itinataguyod ng pamahalaan’ -- Reyes
message: Ayon kay Reyes, kung talagang nais ng administrasyon na maitaguyod ang demokrasya, dapat ay iginagalang nito ang karapatan ng bawat isa na magpahayag.

name: Archbishop Cruz warns enemies of the Church: “Hindi ka tatagal”
message: CBCP president Oscar Cruz said these enemies of the Church should think twice before waging war against them.

name: Nanay pinalayas ng sariling anak sa kanilang mansiyon, pinatira sa kubo na walang tubig at ilaw
message: Ang magulang daw kailanman ay hindi matitiis ang kanilang mga anak, subalit ang anak ay maaaring matiis ang kanilang magulang.

name: Woman in viral road rage also sues cabbie, claims he was the bully
message: She sued the taxi driver for unjust vexation and slight physical injuries; claiming he was the aggressor, was just playing the victim.

name: Aquino proposes bill that allows taxpayers to choose which agency they want their taxes to go
message: The bill will enable taxpayers to allocate 5% of their tax for any of the following: (1) an accredited charity or civil society organization; (2) a priority national or local government project; or (3) a legitimate political party.

name: Robredo, binatikos ang pagkamatay ng mga menor de edad sa 'war on drugs'
message: “Hindi natin maaaring palagpasin ito. Hindi tayo ganito. Hindi ganito ang Pilipino. Kailangang huminto ang walang pakundangang patayan.”

name: Saab Magalona to Duterte supporters: ‘More reason for me to call this admin gross; you will not silence me’
message: On Twitter, she couldn’t help but air her thoughts regarding the EJKs and the recent deaths of minors in Duterte admin’s drug war.

name: De Lima: Mas Matindi pa sa Kamatayan ang Makulong sa Camp Crame
message: “It’s worse than death,” pahayag ni De Lima.

name: Panukalang Batas ni Sen. De Lima: "Bata Bawal Nang Paluin"
message: Layunin ng panukalang batas na ito na iligtas o ilayo ang mga kabataan sa ating bansa mula sa mga pisikal na kaparusahan at lahat ng uri ng panghihiya at pagtratong nakapagpapababa ng sarili.
